# Local developer environment variables.
# Copy values you need into .env for your machine.

# Optional: absolute or repo-relative host path to private internal docs.
# When unset, devcontainer falls back to ./.devcontainer/empty-internal-docs.
DEVCONTAINER_INTERNAL_DOCS_PATH=

# Optional: local observability stack (grafana/otel-lgtm, bundling the OTel
# Collector, Tempo, Prometheus, Loki, and Grafana, plus a standalone Jaeger).
# These services are gated behind the "otel" Compose profile and stay DOWN by
# default, including when the devcontainer auto-starts.
#
# Uncomment BOTH lines below to enable observability persistently: the first brings
# the stack up automatically whenever the devcontainer starts, the second arms the
# WM/ERs to export to the collector (the URL is provided here, so you don't compose it
# yourself). Both are needed — the endpoint is what turns telemetry on, and it is read
# once at WM startup, so (re)open the devcontainer after setting it.
#
# scripts/observability.sh {up,down,status} toggles only the stack (not the endpoint);
# use it to start/stop the collector while the endpoint stays armed.
# COMPOSE_PROFILES=otel
# FINECODE_OTLP_ENDPOINT=http://otel-lgtm:4317
